name: Vessels 166: Story Beat 06
description:
Ed and Bill look dumbfounded; Bill is striding forward to peer at the apparition.
BILL: -WHAT THE FUCK?
23) Close up as Bill reaches down to try to grasp the handle, but his hand-
24) -passes straight through.
25) Wider as Bill staggers back and Ed strides forward in his place, frowning.
BILL: WHAT THE FUCK?
26) Close up on the handle again as Ed’s hand passes through too.
27) Wider as both men take a step back, scratching their heads.
ED: WELL THAT IS A PUZZLE. ALMOST ENOUGH TO PUT A MAN OF HIS RAPIN’. ALMOST…
